  <abstract>Special issue of Concern titled "The Trouble at Highlander". Contains interview with Myles Horton, a story related to litigation by Alice Cobb, and a report on an interview with A. F. Sloan. Also includes reaction letter statements by Eleanor Roosevelt, Roger L. Shinn, John O'Grady, and Reinhold Niebuhr. Cover art by Herschel Pollard shows a scene at the grounds of the school.</abstract>
